track_notes:
Easy trail from Oberlandhütte to Schwarzkogel. Offical signs state 3 hours. 
Forest and grass land trail. Well marked.
Enough space for 40 m dipole and more.

Can be combinded with Kleiner Rettenstein (this makes it a tough tour). See extra track.
Return route shown. August 2019, lift close time is 5.00pm and extended to 8.00pm on Friday
track_title: Hike from the top of the Hahnennhaan Gondola to Schwarzkogel via Penglstein
